postMessage:
Usage:
import { NotesFeed, NoteComposer } from '@/components/crm-notes-system/notes';
import type { Note } from '@/components/crm-notes-system/types';

<NotesFeed notes={notes} currentUserId={userId} onDelete={handleDelete} onEdit={handleEdit} />
<NoteComposer onSubmit={handleCreate} authorName='Jane' />

Note: This uses a simple textarea with @mention detection (no tiptap dependency). For rich text, add tiptap and swap the textarea.
